{"tid":656001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"阿伯狂拍車模遭嘲笑　事後片流出讓網友跪了","createTime":"2018-05-07T00:50:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T04:57:07.000Z","uid":72009,"like":363,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"415ed6e35fe1bcaee6348102d579c19d4d4bd4da","tid":656001,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T00:50:54.000Z","msg":"國外近日瘋傳一段影片，畫面中一位阿伯到車展，二話不說拿起相機就朝美麗的車模狂拍，對方見狀專業地擺出POSE，但可能時間太久也不小心笑場，網友看到影片後更形容「一看阿伯就知道身經百戰，單憑這個步伐就知道他矯健有力，身姿風騷婀娜，雖然一身打扮並不起眼，但看得出他內功深厚！」其他網友看到也跟風嘲笑這位阿伯。<br />\n豈料，近日另段影片曝光，畫面中這名阿伯跟被拍的車模，兩人竟裸著身子躺在床上，而車模還開心地微笑並將頭依偎在阿伯身上。讓不少網友看完後紛紛都閉上了嘴，大讚阿伯「我不應該嘲笑你！」、「這實在是太勵志了！」、「我看完影片直接跪了」。但也有網友眼尖發現，阿伯在車展拍車模時，手上就拎著一大袋現金，感慨地說「事實證明，有錢勝過一切！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180507/640_58f938329ce0ab2658b5a508e99c9f54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180507%2F640_58f938329ce0ab2658b5a508e99c9f54.jpg&h=2fb84d1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180507/640_b3dd4927b430d4051fd6f56db1bf615e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180507%2F640_b3dd4927b430d4051fd6f56db1bf615e.jpg&h=0d7eaa02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n錢就是真愛"},{"pid":"0ecc61d7a59f1affe6a7067b2de9faa9cb601ba9","tid":656001,"uid":26752,"like":334,"dislike":7,"score":327,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T02:37:30.000Z","msg":"條女好撚樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1de5750a7bf293cb62e578917ed74a5e46b3b5c","tid":656001,"uid":150685,"like":343,"dislike":3,"score":340,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T02:42:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1485000/1488328/q5iXpKOWlKSdqqQ_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1485000%2F1488328%2Fq5iXpKOWlKSdqqQ_1024.jpg&h=49ac5c8